 \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"my last competitive dive\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the 30-year-old Daley\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the right time to call it a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley, whose popularity grew even more after he came out as gay in 2013, had won the Olympic gold medal in the men's synchronized 10-meter platform event at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"whose popularity\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's synchronized 10-meter platform event\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really happy with how everything's gone,\\\" an emotional Daley told the BBC.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9067878300534377, \"rank\": 0.06934164330840492, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional Daley\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's always hard when you say goodbye to your sport.\", \"fro